This folder is used to hold earlier versions of this project.

The HTML files will be named and on the folder root. (versionarchives/index_v1.css)
The style CSS files will be under a subfolder called "css". (versionarchives/css/style_v1.css)

please note that in order to make the archived files viewable, I will need to change internal path directories inside the previous versions.
besides directories, nothing will be changed once it is placed inside this folder.
